out\u0022,\u0022time\u0022:63.281386959,\u0022data\u0022:\u0022--- Example 2 ---\\n\u0022}\n,{\u0022stream_name\u0022:\u0022stdout\u0022,\u0022time\u0022:63.281392407,\u0022data\u0022:\u0022Translation: When you wrote me, send me word about how much silver you gave to the palace, but I did not give anything to the palace. As for the proceeds from the silver, the price of the palace is not available. \\n\u0022}\n,{\u0022stream_name\u0022:\u0022stderr\u0022,\u0022time\u0022:66.840342313,\u0022data\u0022:\u0022/usr/local/lib/python3.12/dist-packages/mistune.py:435: SyntaxWarning: invalid escape sequence \u0027\\\\|\u0027\\n\u0022}\n,{\u0022stream_name\u0022:\u0022stderr\u0022,\u0022time\u0022:66.840372613,\u0022data\u0022:\u0022  cells[i][c] = re.sub(\u0027\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\|\u0027, \u0027|\u0027, cell)\\n\u0022}\n,{\u0022stream_name\u0022:\u0022stderr\u0022,\u0022time\u0022:67.04985735,\u0022data\u0022:\u0022/usr/local/lib/python3.12/dist-packages/nbconvert/filters/filter_links.py:36: SyntaxWarning: invalid escape sequence \u0027\\\\_\u0027\\n\u0022}\n,{\u0022stream_name\u0022:\u0022stderr\u0022,\u0022time\u0022:67.049883606,\u0022data\u0022:\u0022  text = re.sub(r\u0027_\u0027, \u0027\\\\_\u0027, text) # Escape underscores in display text\\n\u0022}\n,{\u0022stream_name\u0022:\u0022stderr\u0022,\u0022time\u0022:67.638169712,\u0022data\u0022:\u0022/usr/local/lib/python3.12/dist-packages/traitlets/traitlets.py:2915: FutureWarning: --Exporter.preprocessors=[\\\u0022nbconvert.preprocessors.ExtractOutputPreprocessor\\\u0022] for containers is deprecated in traitlets 5.0. You can pass `--Exporter.preprocessors item` ... multiple times to add items to a list.\\n\u0022}\n,{\u0022stream_name\u0022:\u0022stderr\u0022,\u0022time\u0022:67.638202434,\u0022data\u0022:\u0022  warn(\\n\u0022}\n,{\u0022stream_name\u0022:\u0022stderr\u0022,\u0022time\u0022:67.668940048,\u0022data\u0022:\u0022[NbConvertApp] Converting notebook __script__.ipynb to html\\n\u0022}\n,{\u0022stream_name\u0